general.gigTitle: do custom full fledged website development using react

sellerCard.description: With 4+ years of professional experience and 100+ mobile apps developed, I’m a Full-Stack Mobile and Web developer skilled in React Native, React JS, Node JS, AWS, MongoDB, Firebase, and PostgreSQL. What sets me apart is my collaboration with a dedicated team of developers and designers. Together, we’ve delivered diverse projects across industries like E-commerce, Sports, ERP Solutions, Fashion, ChatGPT, Social Media, Food Delivery, and more.

description.content:
Hey, I will do customized website development for business purposes as per your needs with HTML, CSS, and React

⬇

Development Phases:

  1. Wesite Designs: We will design layout of each screen
  2. Wesite Development: After website design approval we will start developing the screens.
  3. APIs & Database: In parallel with step 2, we will structure the backend and develop APIs for functionalities required.
  4. API Integrations: In this phase, developed APIs will be integrated with the website, and make it functional.
  5. Testing & Deployment: After detailed testing of website and client approval, we will start deploying the web on provided host.

 ⬇

Why me?

130+ orders completed

100% 5-star feedback

Longterm management experience

Best practiced code

 

-- Please contact me before placing a direct order --


Revisions until 100% satisfaction of the Client.


Thank You

-Ibrahim
